{"tid":1271126,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"庫德洛否認華府全面特赦華為　維持列入貿易黑名單","createTime":"2019-07-01T05:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T05:54:05.000Z","uid":147314,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7ef7db19e7658cbe477644af60fd4166aa890b53","tid":1271126,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>庫德洛否認華府全面特赦華為</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=353743\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D353743&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5PgZsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=d5314c4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D353743&h=705fb0ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=353743</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國總統特朗普在中美首腦會談後，同意容許中國電訊設備商華為，恢復向美國企業購買不會影響美國國家安全的零件。白宮經濟顧問庫德洛否認華府是要全面特赦華為。<br />\n<br />\n庫德洛分別接受兩間美國傳媒訪問，他強調總統特朗普不會停止對國家安全的關注，華為仍然被視為美國國家安全的潛在威脅，維持列入貿易黑名單。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普前日在大阪與國家主席習近平會面後，同意為對華為的禁令鬆綁，讓美國企業重新向華為出售零件，不過決定惹來部分國會議員批評，認為特朗普不應該放生華為。<br />\n<br />\n庫德洛表示，商務部將會發出更多出口的臨時許可證，但強調只是批准美國企業向華為出售一些不涉及國家安全敏感技術，而且是世界各地都買得到的晶片或軟件，重申美方只是放寬管制，而非全面特赦。"},{"pid":"91a4974204d019ec8580dbe385b0580c804c1d66","tid":1271126,"uid":147314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:23:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201907010004.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201907010004.aspx&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5PgZsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=db7003c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201907010004.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n柯德洛強調，華為仍在美國的「實體清單」（Entity List）內。實體清單中的外國企業和個人需遵守特定的出口和技術轉移許可規定。<br />\n<br />\n柯德洛表示：「這不是大赦。」他還說：「商務部將在銷售產品普遍可得的情況下，准許一些暫時性的額外許可。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，柯德洛受訪還指出，美中貿易談判沒有時程表，談判可能「持續很長一段時間」。"},{"pid":"4b12fe2c607cae153bed4c5a239e1c07ec31c96b","tid":1271126,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:24:10.000Z","msg":"我見無人post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20318d50c92f43e20b975b2bdcb618b995eed86","tid":1271126,"uid":148987,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:29:31.000Z","msg":"D三毛又要潛"},{"pid":"a7015490bbc6fcf894c45611f95e82a9202cc4a9","tid":1271126,"uid":248131,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:37:07.000Z","msg":"真係撚狗"},{"pid":"618ca10fe2f8d1e9c6ef2d202076cf4b2bf5d6ae","tid":1271126,"uid":41500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"回post唔比三毛打飛機先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be551c432b609e85059792587c3c3a18d7a1f7ed","tid":1271126,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"只係臨時許可證，而且只限於周圍都買到既野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}